ASoC: Intel: Use acpi_dev_present()

Use shiny new acpi_dev_present() and remove all the boilerplate
to search for a particular ACPI device. No functional change.
Cf. 2d12b6b381ba ("ACPI / utils: Add acpi_dev_present()").

